<F P=103> AU2203171794 </F>
<F P=104>  Tirana ATA </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> English </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Tirana, March 22 (ATA) -- The trial of the KOHA 
JONE journalists, Martin Leka and Aleksander Frangaj, requested 
by the prosecutor of the case, Teodor Mosko, was held at the 
Tirana Court of Appeals on March 21. 
  The court did not change the first sentence given to Martin 
Leka, but it sentenced with 5 months imprisonment the KOHA JONE 
editor-in- chief, Aleksander Frangaj, who at the trial of the 
