Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Prague, March 22 (CTK) -- Czech President Vaclav 
Havel said today the process of transformation of the Czech Army 
could be evaluated favorably. "But we will only be able to make 
a definitive assessment after 1995 when the transformation will 
be completed," he told CTK after he visited the army's General 
Staff. 
  Defense Minister Antonin Baudys said that the largest amount 
