Language: <F P=105> English </F>
Article Type:BFN 

<F P=106> ["Pool" item] </F>
  [Text] Brcko, March 24 (TANJUG) -- Bosnian Moslem units 
continued Thursday attacks from heavy infantry weapons on the 
Serb positions in the Brcko region, northeast 
Bosnia-Herzegovina, Bosnian Serb military sources have reported. 
  There were stronger armed provocations during the night of 
Wednesday-Thursday by Moslem and Croat forces against the Serb 
