<F P=102>  AU2403190894 Tirana TVSH Television Network in Albanian 1735 
GMT 24 Mar 94 </F>

<F P=103> AU2403190894 </F>
<F P=104>  Tirana TVSH Television Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Albanian </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] The Albanian Helsinki Committee [KShH] raises its 
voice of protest over the arrest by Serbian police of Kosovar 
publicist and writer Shuaip Beqiri, who is also editor-in-chief 
of the weekly independent FORUMI, which is published in 
Prishtina. 
  The KShH appeals to international institutions to seriously 
assess the dangerous escalation of violence in Kosova, as this 
escalation foreshadows new tragedies that can happen in the 
Balkans and the wider region. 

