  [Text] Pirot, 24 Mar (TANJUG) -- The goal is the 
destruction of all things Slav and of orthodoxy, and that is a 
big war against Russia. You are our first line of defense, 
Aleksandr Vengerovskiy, vice president of the Russian Liberal 
