  [Text] Bratislava, March 23 (CTK) -- In ratio 5:5:4, the 
Democratic Left Party (SDL), the Christian Democratic Movement 
(KDH) and centrist coalition parties proposed their candidates 
for the posts of state secretaries, the press department of the 
