secretaries at the Ministries of Economics, Defense, 
Administration and Privatization of State Property, Education 
and Science, and Agriculture. 
  Jan Lisuch, Roman Vavrik, Sergej Kohut and Ludmila Zimanova 
are the centrist parties' candidates for the posts of state 
secretaries at the Foreign, Justice and Environment Ministries. 

